items.headline: Welcome to The Price is Right Wiki!
items.desc: The Price Is Right Wiki is a collaborative website about the game show on CBS.  The Price Is Right is an American game show centered on the pricing of merchandise and grocery products to win cash and prizes. The wiki format allows anyone to create or edit any article, so we can all work together to create the site.
